This is a modified version of Mischa Spieglemock's XBL (Xbox Live) irc notification bot found here: http://github.com/revmischa/XBL-Notification-Bot

It tracks the Halo: Reach game history of the gamertags specified in the config and sends updates to a irc channel when new game data is available. To have it print out the details of the most recent games of all the gamertags type !reach. Check xbl.yml for config options.